WEBVTT

00:00:00.913 --> 00:00:03.583
Rha Goddess: We are
in a moment of reckoning.

00:00:04.083 --> 00:00:06.335
An epic global plague,

00:00:06.377 --> 00:00:09.255
a massive workforce peace-out

00:00:09.297 --> 00:00:12.091
and a worldwide racial awakening

00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:14.761
have revealed that current
corporate structures

00:00:14.802 --> 00:00:17.805
are not living up
to evolving expectations.

00:00:18.222 --> 00:00:22.185
Work is just not working for most of us,

00:00:22.226 --> 00:00:24.604
especially when it comes
to women of color.

